📁 Project Title: Employee Record Manager using JsonPowerDB
🎯 Objective:
Create a web-based app to manage employee records — add, update, search, and delete — using JsonPowerDB as the backend database.

🛠 Tech Stack:
Layer	Technology
Frontend	HTML, CSS, JavaScript
Backend	JsonPowerDB REST API
Hosting	GitHub Pages (optional)
📋 Features:
➕ Add new employee (ID, Name, Department, Salary)

🔍 Search employee by ID

✏️ Update employee details

❌ Delete employee record

🧹 Reset form fields

✅ Form validation

⚡ Fast response using JsonPowerDB


